                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14597293" author="mreutegg" created="Tue, 23 Jun 2015 07:42:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed changes with test cases and fixes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14598975" author="reschke" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 07:05:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;...resulting in significant performance gains in tests that create many referenceable nodes, such as PackageImportIT (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-3025&quot; title=&quot;add test case simulating batched import of nodes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;OAK-3025&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;OAK-3025&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) and, apparently, XmlImportTest.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14599401" author="dominique.jaeggi" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 13:27:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good to me. AccessControlValidator checks policy nodes, which by definition cannot be hidden nodes. therefore the restriction of the validator to visible nodes only makes total sense.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14599477" author="chaotic" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 14:24:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 from me too. UserValidator may only validate visible nodes (see also &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=anchela&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;anchela&quot;&gt;anchela&lt;/a&gt;&apos;s commit r1475715) - The non-wrapped Validator seems to have been reintroduced by accident.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="14599514" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 14:50:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks a lot for the reviews, I applied the patch to trunk: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1687301&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1687301&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14599628" author="mreutegg" created="Wed, 24 Jun 2015 16:02:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged into 1.2 branch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1687306&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1687306&lt;/a&gt; and 1.0 branch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/r1687316&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/r1687316&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
